  "description": "Filter opens slowly from 5kHz as the envelope decays — at filterEnvAmt 0.45, a 2-second filter decay sweeps through the trefoil resonances like a tide coming in. Medium tangle means the harmonic rotation is active but not overwhelming. Ocean current chorus at 0.3 for gentle detuning motion.",
